project: 1. Shoot the enemies (by clicking mouse left button, "Space" key from keyboard, or tapping the sight icon on the screen).
2. Use arrow keys, or "a", "w", "s", "d" keys from keyboard or the onscreen control keys to control the submarine moving direction.
3. Drive the submarine back to the surface of the sea to load the bullets.
4. Pick up the swimmer and drop the swimmer to the sea surface to get points.
